HEADWORD: Wingless
<hw>Wing"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no wings; not able to
ascend or fly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Wingless bird</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>the
